data.description: Don't miss out on this one bedroom, one bath, unfurnished townhome being offered at the popular Palm Bay Village Complex. Known for its lush, tropical landscaping and lagoon style pool with waterfall, this complex is just minutes from Whitecap Beach, Bob Hall Pier, Packery Channel and the highly anticipated Schlitterbahn Waterpark. This unit features stained concrete floors, Bahama style fans, an open kitchen, dining and living area, covered patio with storage, and assigned parking. Grande cable, internet, telephone, gas grills and a community room are just a few of the added features of Palm Bay Village. Brokered And Advertised By: Coldwell Banker Island Listing Agent: Charlene Beaver
